
### Register (creates user + wallet, returns accessToken)
POST http://localhost:1010/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{

  "firstName": "felix",
  "lastName": "felix",
 "email": "felix.test@example.com",
  "phoneNumber": "+2348012395679",
  "password": "hunter2hunter2"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:1010/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  //  "email": "ada@example.com",
   "email": "olamilekan.test@example.com",
  "password": "hunter2hunter2"
}

### Current user (set accessToken in http-client.env.json)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
